text.__SUMMARY__: Macrozamia lucida is a species of plant in the family Zamiaceae. It is endemic to Australia.
text.Distribution and habitat: This species is found in Southern Queensland, from around Brisbane north to Nambour, in coastal wet sclerophyll forest.
text.References: Whitelock, Loran M. The Cycads. Timber press (2002)  ISBN 0-88192-522-5
